Package: censusindia
Title: Census of India data for R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Saket", "Choudhary", email = "saketkc@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Digitised Census of India data from 1901 to 2011: population time
    series, primary census abstracts at state and district levels, mother
    tongue tables, SC/ST and tribal populations, and administrative
    directories. Census variables can be retrieved with geographic boundaries
    attached for mapping.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://saketlab.github.io/censusindia/, https://github.com/saketlab/censusindia
